OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrancoise Gilot, artist and
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FPicasso's lover, dies      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Francoise Gilot, who emerged from the  
OL,6, shadow of her lover Pablo Picasso to   
OL,7, become acclaimed as an artist in her   
OL,8, own right, has died at the age of 101. 
OL,10,FAn accomplished painter, Gilot also    
OL,11,Fwrote a best-selling 1964 memoir       
OL,12,Fdetailing her tumultuous relationship  
OL,13,Fwith the Spanish giant of modern art.  
OL,15,FShe described the "hell" of being      
OL,16,FPicasso's mistress and artistic muse.  
OL,18,FFrance's culture minister Rima Abdul   
OL,19,FMalak called Gilot "one of the most    
OL,20,Fstriking artists of her generation".   
